Sentencas: The synthesis of nano-sized Ce0.8Y0.18Ca0.02O1.89(YCDC) powders by citrate gel route has been investigated.
Titulo: Chemical Synthesis and Characterization of Ce0.81Y0.18Ca0.02O1.89 as Electrolyte for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The details of gel's combustion I were investigated by TG-DSC and the structure of as-synthesized powders from auto-combustion was characterized by XRD.
Titulo: Chemical Synthesis and Characterization of Ce0.81Y0.18Ca0.02O1.89 as Electrolyte for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The results I show that single phase YCDC powders with average size of 50 nm can be synthesized by citrate gel route.
Titulo: Chemical Synthesis and Characterization of Ce0.81Y0.18Ca0.02O1.89 as Electrolyte for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The as-synthesized powders I exhibited high sinter activity, it can be sintered to 95 % of its theoretical density at 1250 degrees C for 4 h. The YCDC composition exhibits a total I conductivity of 0.02 S/cm at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Chemical Synthesis and Characterization of Ce0.81Y0.18Ca0.02O1.89 as Electrolyte for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
